com.sri.ai.util.math

Class MultinomialIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sri.ai.util.collect.EZIterator<Multinomial>
      • com.sri.ai.util.math.MultinomialIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<Multinomial>

    public class MultinomialIterator
extends EZIterator<Multinomial>
    An Iterator over Multinomials. Provided multinomial is internally kept by iterator and modifiable, so operations on it will reflect on future operations with the iterator.
